# 4. Scale all data between 0 and 1
#    Colour values vary from 0 to 255
data<-fashion_mnist[,-1]/255

# 5. Start kmeans modeling
#    Takes around 15 minutes
start.time <- Sys.time()
cl<-kmeans(fashion_mnist[,-1], centers = 10, nstart = 10, iter.max = 50)
Sys.time() - start.time
